//
// Parity case: a clean project linted via the CLI and the MCP `lint` tool
// should both report zero diagnostics. This guards against either surface
// drifting into spurious warnings.

// @input
<project>
// @surfaces mcp, cli
// @op lint
// @expect-diagnostics 0
